                <footnote.body>
                    <para>
                        <bop/>
                        <bos/>
                        <paratext>The Panel&apos;s deference to the transferee court is especially noticeable.
                            <eos/>
                            <bos/>This deference is noted in §§ <cite.query w-ref-type="NA"
                                                                            w-normalized-cite="MDLITMANs9:2"
